##Hydrographs w/Stage for Oneto-Denier
```{r setup, echo=FALSE, warning=FALSE}
library(knitr)
library(dplyr)
library(htmltools)
library(ggplot2)

MW14$Date <- as.POSIXct(MW14$Date, format = '%m/%d/%y %H:%M')

MW14 <-  read.csv('MW-14_11.2.17.csv', header = TRUE, stringsAsFactors = FALSE)
ggplot() + geom_line(data=MW14, aes(x=MW14$Date, y=MW14$SWL), colour = "purple") +
  labs(x="Date", y="Groundwater Elevation (m)", Title='MW14 Groundwater Elevations')

```
